    "A performance evaluation of seven ML-based classifiers for detection and classification is presented [167].",
    "Machine learning in COVID-19 detectionThis section examines various COVID-19 diagnostic techniques and approaches presently in use.",
    "The information shown in Table 11 was derived from a compilation of publications describing the different ML approaches and their results.COVIDNet is a deep CNN designed to detect COVID-19 in lung X-rays.",
    "They created the COVIDx dataset, which consists of five datasets that are accessible online.",
    "The projected COVID-Net had already been trained on the ImageNet and then trained on the COVIDx dataset."
